	* shared/pci/pci.c, shared/pci/pci.h, shared/pci/pcifinddevice.c:
	Continue PCI API unification. All use pci_find_device(). Also
	reformat to remove tabs.

2005-03-04	Joel Sherrill <joel@OARcorp.com>

